race.description: Taree & Wingham Produce Super Maiden Handicap
race.comment: Strong Super Maiden with plenty of chances. TROUNCE (4) failed to keep up early when resumed with a fast finishing fourth over 1100m at Hawkesbury in fast time. Looking for this trip and further now. Maps well in this weaker contest. Goes close. CALL ME BASIL (1) stuck on gamely at debut in the heavy (8) conditions when a tough third over 1270m at this track. Back without a trial and the winkers go on from the low draw. Must be kept safe. MAXIMUM RIDE (2) ran on and got close first up at Gosford. Fitter for that and the longer distance suits. POSH ANNIE (12) strips fitter now and well placed over this trip. Include from the draw.
